254
00:26:35,740 --> 00:26:39,770
- I have a teacher now.
- Here.

255
00:26:39,770 --> 00:26:42,280
Mom...

256
00:26:42,280 --> 00:26:44,100
I now...

257
00:26:44,100 --> 00:26:46,960
I have a teacher now.

258
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:49,130
My teacher...

259
00:26:49,130 --> 00:26:53,020
