260
00:26:53,020 --> 00:26:55,500
I just met him.

261
00:26:55,500 --> 00:26:59,350
Mom, you probably don't know him either.

262
00:26:59,350 --> 00:27:02,860
He should call you mom, too.

263
00:27:02,860 --> 00:27:05,100
No. No.

264
00:27:05,100 --> 00:27:10,000
He shouldn't call you mom. He's my teacher.

265
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:13,480
He should call you...

266
00:27:21,010 --> 00:27:23,380
You three...

267
00:27:23,380 --> 00:27:25,600
One talks nonstop when drunk.

268
00:27:25,600 --> 00:27:28,250
One only knows how to sit here and smirk.

269
00:27:28,250 --> 00:27:31,150
One has been staring blankly this whole time.

270
00:27:31,150 --> 00:27:33,540
But when you three are together,

271
00:27:33,540 --> 00:27:37,190
it looks comfortable and harmonious.

272
00:27:37,190 --> 00:27:39,460
It's so weird.

273
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:42,800
That's because...

274
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:47,150
we've known each other for so long, so long.

275
00:27:49,010 --> 00:27:51,480
How long?

276
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:55,690
In the past life and this life.

277
00:27:56,630 --> 00:27:58,640
Two life times.

278
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:02,140
You seem drunk, too.

279
00:28:25,170 --> 00:28:28,840
I have a teacher now.

280
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:32,830
Father, our spies reported that since the crown prince returned to the capital,

281
00:29:32,830 --> 00:29:35,780
he will often secretly meet someone named Chai Mu.

282
00:29:37,940 --> 00:29:39,890
Chai Mu?

283
00:29:40,580 --> 00:29:42,250
What's his identity?

284
00:29:42,250 --> 00:29:44,700
This person is very mysterious.

285
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:47,270
Very few people have seen what he really looks like.

286
00:29:47,270 --> 00:29:51,130
Under his control, there is a group called Submerged Dragon Envoys.

287
00:29:51,130 --> 00:29:53,170
Submerged Dragon Envoys?

288
00:29:53,170 --> 00:29:55,570
Yes. It's a Jianghu organization.
(T/N: jianghu- martial arts world or righteous people who follow their own moral principles and not societal laws)

289
00:29:55,570 --> 00:29:57,320
Before, they were seen at the Western Border.

290
00:29:57,320 --> 00:30:00,330
Now, they are seen often in the capital.

291
00:30:00,330 --> 00:30:05,840
That organization called the Submerged Dragon Envoys secretly entered the capital.

292
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:08,550
- What do they want to do?
- I don't dare to speculate.

293
00:30:08,550 --> 00:30:13,300
But according to my investigation, Chai Mu was an acquaintance of Princess Mingyuan.

294
00:30:19,150 --> 00:30:23,100
Make sure to investigate Chai Mu's background thoroughly.

295
00:30:23,100 --> 00:30:25,460
Don't let word get out about it.

296
00:30:25,460 --> 00:30:27,500
Yes.

297
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:30,670
No matter what his goal is, you must find him.

298
00:30:30,670 --> 00:30:32,790
Yes, Your Imperial Majesty.

299
00:30:47,540 --> 00:30:49,140
Yan'er!

300
00:30:52,780 --> 00:30:55,530
Tomorrow is the anniversary of your mother's death.

301
00:30:56,100 --> 00:31:01,040
Together with you, I want to make a cenotaph for her,

302
00:31:01,040 --> 00:31:05,640
so that we can have a place to visit her from now on.

303
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:09,440
I already made a cenotaph for my mother.

304
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:13,550
I don't need irrelevant people to go bother her.

305
00:31:16,340 --> 00:31:18,680
I know you hate me.

306
00:31:19,620 --> 00:31:22,140
Could you give me a little bit more time?

307
00:31:22,140 --> 00:31:25,990
After I finish the things I have on hand, I will take you away from here.

308
00:31:25,990 --> 00:31:29,990
Once some things happen,

309
00:31:29,990 --> 00:31:33,590
it's just like splitting Earth's crust.

310
00:31:33,590 --> 00:31:36,100
It can't be repaired.

311
00:31:38,140 --> 00:31:42,410
Leave. I don't ever want to see you again.

312
00:31:55,330 --> 00:31:58,930
[Singing Jade Brothel]

313
00:31:58,930 --> 00:32:00,840
Let's go. Go.

314
00:32:09,070 --> 00:32:12,730
Sir Chai, right? Please come with me.

315
00:32:17,710 --> 00:32:22,950
Since you are unwilling to cooperate, don't blame us for being rude.

316
00:32:42,230 --> 00:32:44,170
Shenwu Army?

317
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,640
Let's go!

318
00:33:01,410 --> 00:33:03,080
Chase them!

319
00:33:06,060 --> 00:33:08,040
[Mi Luo Drinking House]

320
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:11,400
- Search!
- Get up!

321
00:33:12,030 --> 00:33:14,680
Get up! Get up! Hurry!

322
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:16,310
Get out!

323
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:25,200
- Search from door to door!
- Yes!

324
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:28,410
Get out! Hurry up!

325
00:33:28,410 --> 00:33:30,160
Get out! Get out!

326
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:31,620
Reporting to General, nothing here!

327
00:33:31,620 --> 00:33:33,090
General, nothing!

328
00:33:33,090 --> 00:33:35,980
- Continue searching in front!
- Yes!

329
00:33:37,260 --> 00:33:39,840
How could they do this?

330
00:33:41,330 --> 00:33:44,030
Hurry! Hurry! Come!

331
00:33:47,330 --> 00:33:51,200
Officer! What are you doing, officer?

332
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:54,400
Officer, I'm trying to do business here! Officer!

333
00:33:59,070 --> 00:34:01,730
Don't worry.

334
00:34:01,730 --> 00:34:03,450
What kind of place is back there?

335
00:34:03,450 --> 00:34:06,180
Back there? It's the place where Miss Mingyue lives.

336
00:34:06,180 --> 00:34:09,920
- Miss Mingyue is the top courtesan at our Singing Jade Brothel.
- Come with me!

337
00:34:33,390 --> 00:34:37,340
Who are you? Why did you barge into my room in the middle of the night?

338
00:34:37,340 --> 00:34:39,370
- Search.
- Yes!

339
00:34:50,290 --> 00:34:52,810
General, there's a trace of blood here.

340
00:35:08,860 --> 00:35:10,990
- Arrest her.
- Yes!

341
00:35:11,620 --> 00:35:13,250
- Who are you?
- Move.

342
00:35:13,250 --> 00:35:16,630
- What are you doing? Let go of me!
- Go!

343
00:35:26,190 --> 00:35:31,600
Godfather, if we appear now, it will probably be harmful to Mingyue.

344
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:37,090
What do you want a father like me to do?

345
00:35:38,030 --> 00:35:41,960
Mingyue is intelligent. She'll be all right.

346
00:35:49,660 --> 00:35:53,110
Where is this? Who are you?

347
00:35:54,750 --> 00:35:57,950
I'm the governor of the capital.

348
00:35:57,950 --> 00:36:01,390
My men are trying to capture an important criminal right now.

349
00:36:01,390 --> 00:36:03,610
I will ask you a few questions.

350
00:36:03,610 --> 00:36:06,630
I hope you answer them truthfully.

351
00:36:08,950 --> 00:36:10,300
Who are you?

352
00:36:10,300 --> 00:36:16,370
Officer, I am Mingyue, a courtesan of Singing Jade Brothel.

353
00:36:19,580 --> 00:36:23,330
I heard from my subordinates

354
00:36:23,330 --> 00:36:27,340
that you are the top courtesan at the Singing Jade Brothel.

355
00:36:27,340 --> 00:36:30,890
Every day, you just have one guest. Right?

356
00:36:32,410 --> 00:36:36,460
Who did you see today then? Are you well acquainted with him?

357
00:36:36,460 --> 00:36:38,830
I felt ill today.

358
00:36:38,830 --> 00:36:41,230
I didn't take care of any guests.

359
00:36:41,230 --> 00:36:42,890
Really?

360
00:36:44,410 --> 00:36:48,430
Then, why did my men find a trace of blood in your room

361
00:36:48,430 --> 00:36:52,120
when they were searching for the criminal?

362
00:36:52,120 --> 00:36:54,440
Who does this blood belong to then?

363
00:36:55,330 --> 00:36:58,530
Tonight, I was in my room playing my Chinese lute.

364
00:36:58,530 --> 00:37:02,290
Suddenly, two strangers burst into my room.

365
00:37:02,290 --> 00:37:04,630
They gave me ten taels of silver.

366
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:10,180
They threatened me and told me that my lute sound mustn't stop no matter what was happening outside.

367
00:37:10,180 --> 00:37:13,270
I didn't know that those two were important criminals.

368
00:37:13,270 --> 00:37:17,830
I should thank you for saving my life.

369
00:37:17,830 --> 00:37:21,060
If your men didn't appear at that time,

370
00:37:21,060 --> 00:37:25,200
I'm afraid that I would be dead by now.

371
00:37:29,430 --> 00:37:34,270
Miss, you've spoken well. Water-tight explanation.

372
00:37:34,270 --> 00:37:39,310
Officer, I grew up in the Singing Jade Brothel.

373
00:37:39,310 --> 00:37:42,160
I would never be acquainted with those lawless criminals.

374
00:37:42,160 --> 00:37:45,830
If you don't believe me, you can investigate me.

375
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:54,920
Do you remember what those two looked like then?

376
00:37:56,270 --> 00:38:02,180
Those two men... One was wearing a hood while the other covered his face.

377
00:38:02,180 --> 00:38:05,880
I didn't see their faces properly.

378
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:12,000
But... based on their voice, one was a middle-aged man.

379
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:14,910
Plus, he had a Western Border accent.

380
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:21,460
Western Border accent? Does that mean the man wasn't from the Li Empire?

381
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:23,660
Probably not.

382
00:38:26,770 --> 00:38:29,700
I've asked all my questions.

383
00:38:29,700 --> 00:38:32,480
You must have been frightened today.

384
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:36,670
It's all right. I should thank you for saving me.

385
00:38:40,890 --> 00:38:43,250
I heard that in the capital,

386
00:38:43,250 --> 00:38:46,520
multiple young aristocratic lords

387
00:38:46,520 --> 00:38:51,450
are willing to spend thousands of gold just to listen to you play one song.

388
00:38:51,450 --> 00:38:57,120
You must have amazing musical talents.

389
00:38:57,120 --> 00:39:00,580
I haven't listened to a lute song in a while.

390
00:39:00,580 --> 00:39:06,780
Today, could I have the honor of listening to a song played by you?

391
00:39:08,300 --> 00:39:13,450
No one has ever caused such a big scene just to invite me over and have me play him a song.

392
00:39:13,450 --> 00:39:16,990
What kind of song would you like to hear, Officer?

393
00:39:16,990 --> 00:39:19,660
I'll listen to whatever you're willing to play.

394
00:39:19,660 --> 00:39:21,800
I'll play you the song

395
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:24,080
"Liuyao" then.
(T/N:Liuyao, literal translation 'Minor Sixth' is a song from the Tang Dynasty musical compilation "The Pipa Tune")

396
00:39:24,080 --> 00:39:26,950
- Bring a seat!
- Okay.

397
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:01,340
Who told you to go to a brothel?!

398
00:40:01,340 --> 00:40:02,910
You disobedient thing!

399
00:40:02,910 --> 00:40:06,320
- Father! I really didn't know they were—
- You went to a brothel!

400
00:40:06,320 --> 00:40:10,120
I also didn't know why His Imperial Majesty's Shenwu Army was trying to arrest them!

401
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:11,810
- Father!
- Get away!

402
00:40:11,810 --> 00:40:13,880
