403
00:40:13,880 --> 00:40:15,760
They took...

404
00:40:16,630 --> 00:40:18,920
They took...

405
00:40:18,920 --> 00:40:21,530
Father! Calm down.

406
00:40:21,530 --> 00:40:25,060
I told you not to go to Singing Jade Brothel! But you just have to invite trouble upon yourself!

407
00:40:25,060 --> 00:40:29,260
Father, Mingyue and I have true love between us!

408
00:40:29,260 --> 00:40:31,680
You worthless thing!

409
00:42:03,590 --> 00:42:05,260
Officer!

410
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:12,880
Good!

411
00:42:12,880 --> 00:42:16,660
Just like beads falling into a jade plate. Just like Buddha's voice.
(T/N: Very pleasing and moving sound)

412
00:42:16,660 --> 00:42:20,070
Miss, you played the Chinese lute very well.

413
00:42:20,850 --> 00:42:22,620
Cao Ji.

414
00:42:32,100 --> 00:42:35,610
Take the gold with you.

415
00:42:38,460 --> 00:42:41,320
One can only meet so few bosom friends.

416
00:42:41,320 --> 00:42:46,640
Meeting one is the most valuable thing in life, gold or riches can't compare.

417
00:42:46,640 --> 00:42:49,510
Even though I was born with low status,

418
00:42:49,510 --> 00:42:53,740
I would never try to please anyone just for these earthly items.

419
00:42:55,010 --> 00:42:59,060
Officer, if you really want to hear me play music,

420
00:42:59,060 --> 00:43:01,780
you can come and find me at Singing Jade Brothel.

421
00:43:01,780 --> 00:43:06,110
If I have a chance, I will definitely come to find you at Singing Jade Brothel,

422
00:43:06,110 --> 00:43:10,060
